num_donations: This dataset is state-to-state aggregations of individual contributions from the 2012 election cycle.
Dataset compiled by Dan Lopuch -- github.com/dlopuch
Individual contributions have been filtered to only those targetting Senate or House candidates
(comittee and presidential contributions have been omitted).  Contributions have been further filtered
to include only contributions with a with a different originating state than the candidate's running
state (ie only out of state donations).
The donator's address state is considered the 'donor_state'
total_amount: and the state in which the

num_donations: candidate was running for office in is the 'candidates_state'. 'total_amount' is in USD.
Source: Center for Responsive Politics at OpenSecrets.org.
